# Healthcare Analytics 🏥

## Project Overview

Healthcare Analytics is a data science project that analyzes patient healthcare data to discover insights and build a Machine Learning model for predicting healthcare outcomes.

The project includes data preprocessing, exploratory data analysis, feature engineering, machine learning model development, SQL analysis, Power BI dashboard creation, and deployment using Streamlit.

---

